      "title": "Is Sri Lanka being disabled?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tourism Minister Harin Fernando has said that fuel and gas will be available after July 10 and that the country will return to normalcy, adding that this is not a situation that will paralyze the country.",
        "He was speaking at a media briefing at the Government Information Department tonight."
      ],
